    <question number="1">
        <prompt>What was early capitalism in the colonial period?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">A socialist system</option>
            <option letter="b">A market-based economic system</option>
            <option letter="c">A barter system only</option>
            <option letter="d">A government-controlled economy</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>Early capitalism was a market-based economic system where private individuals and companies controlled trade and industry for profit.</explanation>
