    <question number="4">
        <prompt>How did capitalism affect colonial trade?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">It eliminated all trade</option>
            <option letter="b">It encouraged profit-driven commerce</option>
            <option letter="c">It required government ownership</option>
            <option letter="d">It banned private trading</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>Capitalism encouraged profit-driven commerce and trade, leading to extensive networks of exchange in the colonies.</explanation>
