    <question number="5">
        <prompt>What distinguished colonial capitalism from mercantilism?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Capitalism focused on individual enterprise</option>
            <option letter="b">Capitalism required government control</option>
            <option letter="c">Capitalism prohibited trade</option>
            <option letter="d">Capitalism eliminated private property</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>Colonial capitalism emphasized individual enterprise and market forces, while mercantilism relied on strict government control of the economy.</explanation>
